&lt;li&gt;Lead reviews and presentations for internal and external design reviews regarding electrical systems design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in Process Hazards Analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implementation of hardware following company policies and procedures such as Management of Change and Lock Out/Tag Out.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible work schedule including third shift&lt;/li&gt;
