&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 5 years experience in an I&amp;amp;C development role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with industrial chemical plants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Allen-Bradley, Schneider, Siemens, or Emerson hardware and software&lt;/li&gt;
